@prefix skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .

<http://example.org/dictionary#contact-information--parking-operator_2> a skos:Concept ;
    skos:definition "an appropriate value reflecting whether a parking operator agrees (or not) to make his/her contact information visible to the public."@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "Contact information of the parking operator (for truck parking users)"@en .

